OL,3,CShould dogs be banned from the beach
OL,4,Cat Swansea Bay over the summer?
OL,6,FResidents in Swansea are being
OL,7,Fconsulted on a proposal to ban dogs
OL,8,Ffrom the beach at Swansea Bay during
OL,9,Fthe summer months.
OL,11,FSwansea has more than a dozen of
OL,12,Fbeaches where dogs are welcomed all
OL,13,Fyear round.
OL,15,FBut Swansea Bay may not be one of them
OL,16,Ffor much longer, with a consultation
OL,17,Fcurrently ongoing in which the council
OL,18,Fis seeking residents' views.
