OL,3,CShould dogs be banned from the beach
OL,4,Cat Swansea Bay over the summer?
OL,6,FAround 500 respondents have already
OL,7,Fhad their say, and the local authority
OL,8,Fsays the feedback so far has been
OL,9,Fmixed.
OL,11,FAs part of Swansea Council's aim to
OL,12,Fprovide canine beaches and to ensure
OL,13,Fdog owners keep to specific sections
OL,14,Fof the beach, a bylaw was introduced
OL,15,Fin 1991.
