OL,3,CShould dogs be banned from the beach
OL,4,Cat Swansea Bay over the summer?
OL,6,FThe bylaw excludes dogs from specific
OL,7,Fbeaches on Gower and sections of
OL,8,FSwansea Bay between the months of May
OL,9,Fand September, and excludes dogs from
OL,10,Fthe beach from the West Pier to the
OL,11,Feastern edge of the slip opposite the
OL,12,FSwansea Municipal Baths.
OL,14,FA second bylaw was introduced in 1998
OL,15,Fexcluding dogs from the slip opposite
OL,16,FWest Cross Inn to the beach access
OL,17,Fpoint opposite Sketty Lane.
